description: Unveiling the CLB KIDZ Ordinal Collection: 2500 raw, hand-drawn artworks shattering digital sterility, a fierce rebellion against norms. Your badge of honor in the Web3 battle, it signifies defiance. In the OutKast Lounge, access rebellious gatherings, gritty rewards, and the alluring HiLo Ballerz game. You possess the keys to this shadowy elite realm.
